    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are acceptable under MRL 2 guidance. Uncertainty quantification was completed with a Monte Carlo propagation of 200 samples, and a screening sensitivity study was described in the UQ narrative identifying rotational speed and inlet hematocrit as dominant drivers. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 was confirmed at the worst-case operating point. The overall credibility body of evidence supports acceptance of the CFD model for the stated COU.",
